{"tid":1474203,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"華為手機時區列台灣為國家 中國網民崩潰怒吼失望","createTime":"2019-08-15T05:43:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T06:03:21.000Z","uid":56533,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c1e7eace5ab81153744f3444929f3aba81a30282","tid":1474203,"uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T05:43:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2425000/2426707/600_phpU5kCWf_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2425000%2F2426707%2F600_phpU5kCWf_1024.jpg&h=79d621af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n過往好些公司或品牌，都曾將台灣、香港等地方列為「國家」，引發中國政府及部份內地網民不滿。近日捲入這類紛爭的，除了有水晶首飾品牌 Swarovski、時尚品牌 Versace 外，竟然還有華為。早前有網民發現，部份型號的華為手機在設定時區、國家時，若使用簡體字時，台北被稱作「中國台北」，但切換到繁體字時卻變成「台灣台北」，讓好些內地網民相當憤怒。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日前有內地網民發現，華為獨立子品牌「榮耀」（Honor），在設定時區、國家時，若使用簡體字語系就會顯示「中國台北」；不過當改成繁體字語系時，台北就成了「台灣台北」。如果選擇香港或澳門，則仍會出現「中華人民共和國」。除了榮耀，網民陸續查看其他華為型號手機，有指 P30、nove5 pro、nova4 等的部份版本，亦出現了相同的情況。<br />\n<br />\n消息傳開後，不少內地網民質疑華為「雙重標準」，「想兩邊討好」，怒吼：「華為，你太讓我失望了」、「請問華為什麼時候道歉？為什麼一直刪回覆？怎麼還不道歉？」、「出來道個歉有這麼難嗎？」「傷害民族感情」、「垃圾華為」等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2426707/%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E6%99%82%E5%8D%80%E5%88%97%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E7%82%BA%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%20%20%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E5%B4%A9%E6%BD%B0%E6%80%92%E5%90%BC%E5%A4%B1%E6%9C%9B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2426707%2F%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%258D%2580%25E5%2588%2597%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E7%2582%25BA%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%25B6%2520%2520%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25B4%25A9%25E6%25BD%25B0%25E6%2580%2592%25E5%2590%25BC%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E6%259C%259B&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdhzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=44d2cb73\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2426707/%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E6%99%82%E5%8D%80%E5%88%97%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E7%82%BA%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%20%20%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E5%B4%A9%E6%BD%B0%E6%80%92%E5%90%BC%E5%A4%B1%E6%9C%9B</a>"},{"pid":"9753966de4f5d02c9a319f7afdf7c0e42fc59682","tid":1474203,"uid":212217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T05:44:14.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">求推求推! 香港人可以同時試下「節奏抗爭」noise making protest!</span> </strong><br />\n<br />\n[推膠招]全民係屋企都可以示威:Noise-Making抗爭法<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1469010\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1469010</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wLUm0vt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwLUm0vt.jpg&h=01e3d423&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c4a3dd3428f709178324c463a13ddd42bac8ab27","tid":1474203,"uid":129013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T05:44:35.000Z","msg":"只要繼續將佢地嘅愛國主義推到最最最極端<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2554159bbabd00c49d099d0e04540a056ff7bce","tid":1474203,"uid":120715,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T05:44:59.000Z","msg":"班蝗想借啲二買其他牌子手機姐"},{"pid":"699b186a1efa3b6cfff3cfe5d47ec798f279ae64","tid":1474203,"uid":25601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T05:45:27.000Z","msg":"引導佢地抵制華為"},{"pid":"07ba5296f69054eb0808f76d6fb059f481efdef0","tid":1474203,"uid":258208,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T05:45:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />愛國就要抵制華為"},{"pid":"efd4418f34318ad4c83ea797890c494d4f639d25","tid":1474203,"uid":21108,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T05:46:43